      "writtenOn": "2020-07-08T08:49:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Fixtures don\u0027t need to declare software/hardware dependencies. Tests need them because some tests should be skipped even if they\u0027re selected by attribute expressions. OTOH fixtures can\u0027t be \"skipped\" when any test depending on them are being run.",
